he first slide. The nav table should use `first` / `home` only.\n5. **Timer commands not documented** — `start`/`go`, `pause`/`stop`, `reset` are usable commands with no mention.\n\n---\n\n**Recommended additions:**\n\n```diff\n ## Project Structure\n\n src/\n ├── App.tsx                    # Slide definitions\n ├── main.tsx                   # React entry point\n ├── index.css                  # Global styles & font import\n ├── vite-env.d.ts              # Vite type declarations\n ├── types/\n │   └── slides.ts              # TypeScript interfaces\n+├── slides/\n+│   ├── index.ts               # Re-exports all slides\n+│   ├── TitleSlide.tsx         # Individual slide components\n+│   ├── IntroSlide.tsx         # (35 slides total)\n+│   └── ...\n+├── prompts/\n+│   └── *.json                 # Animated/structured slide content data\n ├── hooks/\n-│   └── useSlideNavigation.ts  # Navigation state & command parsing\n+│   ├── useSlideNavigation.ts  # Navigation state & command parsing\n+│   └── useTouchNavigation.ts  # Swipe gesture support\n ├── components/\n │   ├── Presentation.tsx       # Main container component\n │   ├── Slide.tsx              # Fullscreen slide wrapper\n │   ├── TerminalInput.tsx      # Command input box\n │   ├── CodeBlock.tsx          # Syntax-highlighted code\n │   ├── SlideProgress.tsx      # Slide counter\n-│   └── OnboardingTooltip.tsx  # Navigation help tooltip\n+│   ├── OnboardingTooltip.tsx  # Navigation help tooltip\n+│   ├── PointerTooltip.tsx     # Contextual pointer hints\n+│   ├── SlideElements.tsx      # Reusable slide building blocks\n+│   └── Timer.tsx              # Presentation timer\n```\n\n```diff\n ## Adding Slides\n\n-Edit `src/App.tsx` and add to the `slides` array:\n+Each slide is a separate component in `src/slides/`. To add a new slide:\n+\n+1. Create `src/slides/MySlide.tsx`\n+2. Export it from `src/slides/index.ts`\n+3. Import and add to the `slides` array in `src/App.tsx`\n```\n\n```diff\n ## Navigation Commands\n\n Type in the input box:\n - `next` or `n` → Next slide\n - `prev`, `back`, `p`, `b` → Previous slide\n - Number (e.g., `3`) → Go to slide 3\n-- `first`, `start`, `home` → First slide\n+- `first`, `home` → First slide\n - `last`, `end` → Last slide\n - `reveal` or `r` → Reveal next content stage\n+\n+Timer commands:\n+- `start` or `go` → Start timer\n+- `pause` or `stop` → Pause timer\n+- `reset` → Reset timer and clear IntroSlide tool selections\n```\n\n---\n\nShall I apply these updates?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2250,"cache_read_input_tokens":40085,"output_tokens":1578,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2250,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYr6Kwq8SYx1wqS5WoF5V","type":"assistant","uuid":"3e387dc7-83a0-4b41-99b8-7e3f0c0ac483","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:33:41.029Z"}
